        "fontFamily": "Verdana",
        "fontSize": 10,
        "textColor": "#000000",
        "label": "After you have completed entering information into this purchase order you will want to print it. Do the following:\n1 - place your cursor over the word “file” in the main navigation bar and click\n2 - a drop down menu will appear\n3 - Click on the word “Page Setup”\n4 - You will see categories where, when you click on them, drop down menu’s will appear.  You should fill in the followinf choices;\n     Format For:  HP LaserJet 3390\n     Orientation:  Make sure the first block is highlighted\n     Scale:  100%\n - then click on the blue oblong in the right bottom corner. \n5 - place your cursor over the word “file” again as you did in step one\n6 - a drop down menu will appear\n7 - click on the word “print” - this is right below the “Page Setup”\n8 - A window will appear with options will appear\n9 - first make sure that the printer listed is the HP LaserJet 3390\n10 - Designate the number of copies you want by clicking in the box and typing in the number\n11 - Click on the button next to the word: “From” and then type in a 1 in the first window and then click in the second window and type a 1 there also.  This makes it so you only print the first page.\n12 - finally click on the blue “Print” button in the buttom right corner of the window.\n\nYour purchase order will now print.",
